archimate:Product.name: Architecture repository
archimate:Product.documentation: Architecture Repository (beslutninger tatt i preliminary state) - Tailered Architeture Framework * Architecture Metamodel - architecture method - content metamodel * Architecture Capability (beslutninger tatt i preliminary state) - Organizational model for Enterprise Architecture - skills repository (kompetanse) - organization structure - architecture charter * Architecture Landscape - strategic architecture - segment architecture - capability architecture * Reference Libaray - organization reference materials (maler) hentet utenfra eller laget selv for å ha noe å gjenbruke. Første runden er tøffest siden du ikke har denne. * Standards information base - business standards - data standards - application standards - technology standards * Governance Log - uttrykk for architecture boards sine aktiviteter - decision log - compliance assessments - capability assessment - calendar - project protifollio - performance measurement
